@FileProcessorApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5299
@ApiKey = super-secret-key-123

### Get processing report
GET {{FileProcessorApi_HostAddress}}/api/files/report
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Get report WITHOUT key (should return 401)
GET {{FileProcessorApi_HostAddress}}/api/files/report
Accept: application/json

### Upload and process a CSV file
POST {{FileProcessorApi_HostAddress}}/api/files/process?column=Amount
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

Name,Amount
Alice,100
Bob,250.5
Carol,49.5
------Boundary--